divs: Sighting DetailsLarge silver object partially shrouded in clouds moved from north to south across the horizon near EW Tollway 88 and Rte. 39 Downers Grove IL Might have been a blimp but it seemed to large and moved to quickly Wasn't a plane .. no wings. Moved southerly and then westerly and then disappeared. Wierdest thing I have ever seen.
trends: There have been 3 other sightings in Downers Grove
There were no other sightings in Downers Grove on or around March 7th 2007
Summary: Object moved north to south across the horizon at a speed to fast to be a blimp.
